Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:24.90,標題,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}「人魚族的同居日常」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.92,0:01:31.92,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,brume0425僅分享於伊莉論壇/動畫下載區(免空)請勿任意轉載
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:33.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,緊急事態!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.00,0:01:37.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我們所保護的史萊姆 蘇的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:39.66,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,被政府發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:42.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但對方擁有國家權力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:43.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,該怎麼對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:46.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling參謀 有什麼解決方案嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:48.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,別突然把問題丟給我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:50.89,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,感覺妳們突然變成蘇的同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.89,0:01:56.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為‧‧‧這孩子不會成為爭奪Darling的對手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.83,0:02:00.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我只服從主公的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.46,0:02:03.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我是他種族交流法保安局的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.73,0:02:04.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:08.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,來留主先生 多謝平日的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:09.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,失禮了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:16.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,大家呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:21.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,收留了這麼多留學生寄宿 真是出色的宿主呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.43,0:02:24.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,蘇的房間?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:27.61,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什麼啊 墨須小姐原來也有意外溫柔的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:32.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,到這裡應該就沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:35.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在風波平息前就先藏起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:38.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我說我說 我們丟下主人沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:41.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,糟糕! 把那麼重要的事給忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:44.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒跟Darling在一起的話 我們也會被逮捕的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:46.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快藏起來!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:50.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,找到了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:51.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒有 找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:52.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,到底去哪裡了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:53.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,去那邊找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:54.88,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:56.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,追兵嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:57.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,來的異常的快?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:00.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,帕皮?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:05.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳在做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:09.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為蘇想喝水 就把瓶裝水‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:13.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,馬上就乾了 忍耐一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:14.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這次又怎‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:22.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧妳要幹什麼? 蘇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是在舔取水份嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:31.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧等一下 蘇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.22,0:03:36.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,想喝水的話我會幫妳拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:40.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快. . .快住手  蘇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.06,0:03:45.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好‧‧‧好像 帕皮 好像‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:52.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這個是!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:54.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,濕了的話  會被幹掉!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的 到底去哪了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:04:01.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,難得墨須小姐準備蘇的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:05.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,誰‧‧‧誰來?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:07.56,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,請來救救我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:08.66,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,誰來‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,軟軟的安全氣曩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你‧‧‧你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:25.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,要叫救護車來媽?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.35,0:04:28.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,平常都會有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:35.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,謝謝您在危急關頭救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:38.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,請容我自我介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我叫做梅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:42.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真的十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.32,0:04:43.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳‧‧‧妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:45.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我叫來留主公人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:47.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼我就到這
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.17,0:04:49.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我還在尋找他種族的女孩們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:54.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,莫非是哈米亞族‧哈耳庇厄族‧半人馬族的女孩們嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:56.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那樣的話 我剛才看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:01.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真頭痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:04.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒想到脫水的蘇這麼難處理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:07.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,黑衣人也變多了 怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:11.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,既然這樣只能趁他們不注意移動到別處了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:13.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳那是什麼表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:18.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,還有其他能藏身的地方嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.32,0:05:21.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為珊卓雷雅屁股很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:23.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳的尾巴也不是很長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:28.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呀啊啊 弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:29.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,囉嗦!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:32.12,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我沒想到那裡有水龍頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,濕成這樣好厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就像是失禁一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:44.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,喂 等‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:46.65,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快住手 蘇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:48.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,想喝水去水龍頭那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:51.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不能發出聲音!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:52.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,會被發現的!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:55.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,加油 珊卓雷雅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:58.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,只要吸收完水份 蘇就會安靜下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:04.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,口水‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:15.16,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,珊卓雷雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:22.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎‧‧‧怎麼了 從公園傳來了好強的殺氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:28.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,既然如此 就來持久戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:30.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,奉陪到底了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:32.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,話說 去喝那邊的水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:40.77,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳在做什麼呢 米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:44.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這‧‧‧這是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:46.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,蘇‧‧‧襲‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:51.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,明明身上哪裡都沒濕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:56.33,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,糟糕!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:06.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,為什麼知道我的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:10.68,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Da‧‧‧Darling  不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.19,0:07:22.27,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦! 我也‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:30.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不愧是已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:38.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼防水房間就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:41.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:43.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼辛苦究竟為了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.88,0:07:45.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,太好了  蘇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:49.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,拜託您明天簽好這裡的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.22,0:07:54.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,裝修完成了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨須小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:59.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,求妳不要只安排施工卻完全不露面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:01.68,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨須小姐 墨須小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:05.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,謝謝妳為了蘇建造了房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:06.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,聽好了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.34,0:08:09.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我可是要做各種工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:11.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,又要幫留學生找寄宿家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:13.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,又要監視是否有人違反他種族交流法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,又要執行新的方案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:16.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但薪水卻沒漲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.45,0:08:17.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再加上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,偷渡入境和新他種族什麼的‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:23.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,說實話 乾脆就不管了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:25.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:29.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以我對史萊姆的他種族什麼的看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.35,0:08:30.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,請多指教!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.25,0:08:31.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這樣可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:32.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:34.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嘛 太好了 蘇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:38.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那為什麼要幫蘇建造房間呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.22,0:08:40.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:42.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哦~個房間是‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:45.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,失禮了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:50.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,大家貴安!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:53.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哎 為什麼妳會在這裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:55.66,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳擅自外出讓我們很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:57.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳知道我們找妳找的有多辛苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:08:59.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:03.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是無論如何我都想看看城市的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:07.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,然後偶然 被寄宿家庭的人救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:09.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,簡直就是命運
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:11.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,寄宿家庭?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:13.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是說要寄宿到我家嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:13.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那Darling君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在正式介紹一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:19.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這孩子是‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:26.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我是人魚族的美洛努‧羅雷萊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:30.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,今天開始寄宿在您家中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,請您多多指教!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:35.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,老爺!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}魔物娘!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:44.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0000FF&}魔物娘!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:51.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這樣可以嗎? 梅洛小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:54.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,請叫我美洛 老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:58.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯 一起去吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:02.31,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:05.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你在做什麼 跟她卿卿我我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.19,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧米亞 妳在幹什?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,您沒事吧 老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:18.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,等‧‧‧要擔心Darling的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:27.96,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的 妳在幹什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:31.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我抱著她只是帶她去去二樓看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,可‧‧‧可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:37.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,墨須小姐說待會會把新輪椅拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:40.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,在那之前我來抱她走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:41.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Da‧‧‧Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞 妳怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:46.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,都是寄宿的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:47.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:51.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,爭奪Darling的對手又增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:53.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎麼可能還那麼悠閒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:56.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,到目前為止因為 珊卓雷雅也沒有越過界線
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:57.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而帕皮只是個小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:10:59.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,蘇的話 在問題外!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:02.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我才能站在候補新娘第一這個位置
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:05.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳是這麼看我們的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:09.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,再說她也不一定有那種想法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:11.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好棒的宅邸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:15.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,話說回來 老爺你有戀人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:17.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,瞄準了!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳‧‧‧妳突然問什‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:25.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:28.45,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,事發突然不小心‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:34.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling 真色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:35.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,你是故意的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:36.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不‧‧‧不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:40.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不‧‧‧人魚的身體為了防止乾燥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,上面佈滿了黏液
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:46.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以衣服會滑落也是常有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:48.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而且‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.76,0:11:51.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,如果是老爺的話 那個‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:53.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:56.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,已經開始攻略了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,可惡‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:01.70,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,黏黏滑滑的人有蘇就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,黏液啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.23,0:12:05.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以蘇才襲擊了她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:09.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,蘇~和姊姊去那邊玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這裡是客房
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:12.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那麼接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:13.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:15.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,討厭~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:17.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不要這麼盯著我看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:20.74,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我跟蘇一起玩後全身就濕濕黏黏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:23.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,以眼還眼 以牙還牙!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:24.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,以濕滑還濕滑!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:28.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我不會把Darling讓給妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:31.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那樣的話‧‧‧去洗個澡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:32.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,熱水已經放好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:36.19,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,可惡的Darling! 居然這麼體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我最喜歡你這點了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:39.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是這樣下去會如那傢伙所願了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:42.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞 妳有點意識過剩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:43.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,, 妳再說什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:46.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她突然來寄宿 還對Darling拋媚眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:48.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,背裡肯定有什麼陰謀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:51.40,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,無論如荷也不能讓Darling被她搶走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:55.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,既然如此 就用空調讓房間變冷!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,為身為人魚‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.85,0:13:00.91,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,而穿泳衣‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:05.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,感~到~後~悔~吧~!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:07.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,難道不是妳在後悔嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎感覺有點冷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:12.58,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,今天有這麼冷嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:13.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,梅洛妳不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:17.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是 人魚對低溫有抗性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:18.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,只是小事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:22.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,睡著會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是不是再冬眠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:25.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什麼啊 原來開了空調了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:30.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,哇! 設定的溫度好高
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:31.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦? 不會動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:33.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是沒電了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:41.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:46.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,既然如此我們三人合力保護Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:48.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳想把我們也牽扯進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:50.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我們是競爭對手也是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,帕皮也會來幫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.98,0:13:55.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,吶‧‧‧來玩遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.37,0:13:56.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,瞬間脫離?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:13:57.93,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,帕皮小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:14:01.13,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,老爺有戀愛的對象了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:08.35,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,看來妳很擔心主公的男女關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.77,0:14:11.15,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳對這類話題很感興趣?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.15,0:14:13.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是 雖然有點害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:17.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為人魚公主的童話在人魚之間很受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,人魚公主是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:21.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是一個愛上人類王子的人魚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:24.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,用她的歌聲為代價
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,變成了人類
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:26.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,結果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:31.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,未能實現戀情而成泡沫消失的悲傷戀愛故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,人魚們都對Love的羅曼史沒有抵抗力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:40.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我也經常會去看演繹悲傷戀愛的歌劇或音樂劇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:43.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,歌劇或音樂劇‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,無論是妳說話方式或禮儀舉止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.86,0:14:49.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,特別是身上散發的氛圍 和一般人差太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:52.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,況且那個隨意的墨須小姐居然對妳‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:54.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,還使用了敬語
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.10,0:14:57.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,實在很讓人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.22,0:14:59.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不愧是珊卓雷亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:01.19,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,總感覺很可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:06.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,珊卓雷雅小姐是老爺的戀人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:06.69,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,什!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:10.25,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,戀戀戀‧‧‧戀人什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:12.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我只是侍奉主公之人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:14.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,和傳聞中的一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:19.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我聽說半人馬族是很有榮耀感的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:23.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我能從妳身上感受到更高貴的信念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:25.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:27.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,就像是宣誓對主公絕對的忠誠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,中世紀的騎士一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:32.92,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎麼回事? 這傢伙釋放出的氣場‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:36.47,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,簡直就像是在一國之主面前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:42.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,從未奢求過能遇見像妳這樣有著高貴榮譽感的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:46.11,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,感謝這如同奇蹟般的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:48.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,珊卓雷雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:49.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊‧‧‧是!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:52.36,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,期待妳今後還能盡己所能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:54.30,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是! 就算粉身碎骨‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:56.24,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快回來 中世紀的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:57.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,呃‧‧‧我到底怎麼‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:00.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真是的 總之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:03.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我絕對不會把Darling讓給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:03.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳明白了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:07.85,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我並沒有那個意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:13.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,絕對! 不會發生那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.69,0:16:16.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好熱 我找到電池了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:18.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,梅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.78,0:16:19.97,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:24.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,人魚只要讓鰓保持濕潤 也能在陸地上呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:26.83,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但暖氣讓空氣變乾燥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:28.52,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那我帶妳回房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.52,0:16:30.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,非常謝謝 老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:32.81,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞 拜託妳換電池了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:38.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她絕對在策劃些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:41.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞 妳適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:46.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,都是妳弄壞了輪椅 主公才會一直照顧她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:50.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,憧憬童話的人又不只她一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:50.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.27,0:16:55.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,童話中的公主一定會被王子所救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:17:00.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,之後公主和王子會一直幸福地生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.08,0:17:04.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所以我的夢想就是被王子公主抱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:08.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我也能被王子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:10.57,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:14.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那個人魚卻享受著Darling的公主抱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:17.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這從物理上來說不太可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:21.77,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那傢伙 用泳衣來誘惑Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:24.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那妳也穿上泳衣不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:31.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,老爺真的沒有戀人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:33.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒‧‧‧沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:35.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳為什麼那麼在意?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:36.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那是因為‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:39.51,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:47.18,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這個泳池果然好大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:49.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我想來游泳 可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:50.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯~請
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:52.48,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,吶~Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:54.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,一起來游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:55.49,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不‧‧‧不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:57.90,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這樣就站到同一起跑點上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:18:00.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不如說露出度是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:02.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,絕對不會讓妳為所欲為了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:04.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那‧‧‧那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.10,0:18:07.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳在幹什麼? 快點進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:10.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不‧‧‧不是‧‧‧那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:12.34,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不必那麼介意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:13.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那‧‧‧.那就
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:21.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,被妳給誘惑了該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:24.01,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,還不是妳借我的泳衣太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:27.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那條特大號的沙灘巾在哪裡找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:30.77,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這是‧‧‧那個‧‧‧床單
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:32.82,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳在幹什麼? 帕皮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.82,0:18:34.53,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,蘇 不知道去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:36.46,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她在不在這裡面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:38.03,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,怎麼可能在!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:43.73,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,失‧‧‧失陪了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:47.04,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,她們到底是來做什麼的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.90,0:18:48.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:50.79,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這樣叛徒就‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:55.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:58.80,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那傢伙露出本性了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:00.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,別對Darling出手!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:03.05,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好深
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:05.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,好冷‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Da‧‧‧Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:11.41,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不妙!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:13.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,體溫在下降
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:14.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,身體要動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:18.22,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,別說要救Darling了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:18.99,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我自己都. . .
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:23.26,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Da‧‧‧Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:30.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:35.42,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:48.87,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,謝謝 Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:49.75,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不要緊吧 米亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:53.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,啊 怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:55.39,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,身體居然這麼冰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:58.44,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,讓我用我的體溫給妳溫暖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:19:59.29,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:01.10,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,梅洛小姐 冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:04.88,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,米亞 浴池水還熱的可以直接進去泡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:06.94,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,嗯嗯‧‧‧  蘇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:09.14,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,快住手 蘇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:10.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,暖氣把她也哄乾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:12.71,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,看來好像在尋找水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:16.21,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,剛才也是 突然朝我飛過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:19.43,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是‧‧‧是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.14,0:20:22.50,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,先去泡澡 米亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:25.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我也一起 可以嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:30.63,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,真暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:34.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,這就是這個國家所說的坦誠相見嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:35.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,梅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:37.08,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,那個‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:40.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,對不起 對妳做了很多失禮的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:42.62,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.62,0:20:43.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,妳沒發現嗎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.10,0:20:48.06,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,因為梅洛很自然的和Darling那麼要好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:49.86,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,讓我有點吃醋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:51.37,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:52.59,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,但是‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:58.20,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling的新娘寶座我是不會讓給妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:20:59.55,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,絕對不會!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:00.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,新娘?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:03.78,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不 我並沒有那樣的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:06.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我不是說過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:09.64,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我很憧憬人魚公主那種羅曼史‧‧‧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:11.09,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:12.07,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:13.84,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我非常憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:17.38,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,像人魚公主那樣的‧‧‧悲戀!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:20.95,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我不會妨礙米亞小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.95,0:21:24.32,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不對 不如說我衷心祝福妳能和老爺結合
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:26.54,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我想要談一場悲戀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:30.17,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,想要向老爺獻上絕不會沒有回報的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.17,0:21:34.00,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,所‧‧‧所以我會做為情人為大家應援的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:39.02,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,不過希望妳們能容忍一下老爺的出軌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:43.76,Default-b,brume0425,0,0,0,,Darling是我一個人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:43.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,梅洛 讓人不能大意的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:48.76,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,已經那麼要好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:22.60,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,我連蛻皮都蛻不好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.81,0:23:27.23,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&HA0CCF9&\3c&H000000&}難得Darling肯令正式我們 認真考慮結婚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:28.98,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&HA0CCF9&\3c&H000000&}我卻無法做出回應
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.98,0:23:30.28,Default,brume0425,0,0,0,,{\c&HA0CCF9&\3c&H000000&}真是太丟臉了
